Dialpad Meetings is the only meeting platform that’s ditched pins and downloads to deliver the easiest path to collaboration.

Features that Matter:

Join Meetings from Anywhere
Join an existing meeting or start a new one right from your Android device.

See Your Meetings with Live Video
Live video ensures that you’re able to fully interact with other participants in real-time during a meeting, and picture-in-picture support lets you multitask by unlocking both video and audio while outside the Dialpad Meetings app.

No Pins, No Problems
Never fumble with lengthy, complicated PINs to join a meeting.

Know Who’s On
With displayed participant cards, never question who’s joined the call or speaking. Opt to lock your meeting once everyone’s joined to add an extra level of security.

Get The Full Picture
View screenshare and gain the full context of what’s being discussed.

Contact Syncing
Display profile details including surfaced insights from CRMs like Salesforce

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

• Added ability to send images to Meetings chat, including gallery photos, camera capture, and GIFs.
• Improved call audio experience, including disabling the proximity sensor while participating via speaker, and showing the proper icon for the current audio source.
